{"tid":372423,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"部iphone比車碌過","createTime":"2017-08-24T10:07:26.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-25T20:43:48.000Z","uid":48628,"like":7,"dislike":44,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"153133126e5b9786328f2bd329c214ab4d560796","tid":372423,"uid":48628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:07:26.000Z","msg":"尋晚趺左部機係馬路，見到已經救唔切，說時慢那時快，即刻有架七人車碌過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但竟然！！！除左mon貼爆咩事都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我係講真，勁撚誇張<br />\n抵apple成主流手機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但雖然外觀無咩，有時禁啲app會hang機，禁唔到要重新開機先得，同埋機身勁熱<br />\n有無人知咩原因<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我想用部機多一排先 因為岩岩換完電<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：非打手"},{"pid":"11099685068a99e7c3af5e13cc0fd43eff1154f1","tid":372423,"uid":3241,"like":18,"dislike":2,"score":16,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:08:43.000Z","msg":"冇圖你老母對波比人碌過都係咁話"},{"pid":"12c8e1b4557b1a60a0af637c4166bf3a177e8dd4","tid":372423,"uid":82917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:10:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇圖你老母對波比人碌過都係咁話</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbe1dedbfd12fe49e95a224ca8d74cdc010d2cb4","tid":372423,"uid":48628,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:13:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇圖你老母對波比人碌過都係咁話</blockquote><br />\n我得一部電話，點比圖，影黎都無用，因為真係咩事都無，機身花都係之前整落<br />\n<br />\n補充：我仲要裸機無case<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5f47f2d3a499755bfcc28fc36a375ff5dba4c30","tid":372423,"uid":48628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:19:25.000Z","msg":"其實主要想問點解會碌完會hang機同發熱<br />\n有無解決方法"},{"pid":"32cc67652ecd2b83d4a7b3fe444e7354223c3b81","tid":372423,"uid":62063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:22:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實主要想問點解會碌完會hang機同發熱<br />\n有無解決方法</blockquote><br />\n內傷=乜事都冇？<br />\n利申：iPhone user"},{"pid":"196a371eb62d6f5950b6c95704b007ff27c7f562","tid":372423,"uid":48628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:24:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實主要想問點解會碌完會hang機同發熱<br />\n有無解決方法</blockquote><br />\n內傷=乜事都冇？<br />\n利申：iPhone user</blockquote><br />\n應該都係，好在每次入app禁野hang重新開機就用到"},{"pid":"3080cb3d6454b0e347feca422597a10c0bbd3f80","tid":372423,"uid":26451,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T10:47:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2fa5b8723c40e893559f4fd15c6eaa71ca3c54e9","tid":372423,"uid":13194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:18:55.000Z","msg":"機身發熱其實好危險<br />\n小心啲好"},{"pid":"965871fd2952eee73f39f51c1a723bba65ca366d","tid":372423,"uid":75768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:24:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>機身發熱其實好危險<br />\n小心啲好</blockquote><br />\n隨時爆"},{"pid":"06d26c719265805e97eb7fcbdda92da299b2262f","tid":372423,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:27:42.000Z","msg":"iphone4係幾硬"},{"pid":"b48fc590d44b22c97573d9abddc828a67ea1c9b8","tid":372423,"uid":5159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T11:36:01.000Z","msg":"cap 張圖上黎睇下<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82bb8a7064de4ce2ccfba268779fc49193c3f049","tid":372423,"uid":113042,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-24T12:14:01.000Z","msg":"圖定老母？"},